{"tid":954110,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有正職, 想考返個的士牌part time揸的士","createTime":"2018-12-24T11:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T05:04:45.000Z","uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2798af464749805558fa9037a5797fa3204c2311","tid":954110,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"上年考到車牌之後冇揸過車<br />\n如果特登買架車黎揸太奢侈啦<br />\n因為住得近平時又冇地方周圍去<br />\n成日想搵個理由俾自己揸下車<br />\n忽發其想 不如考牌揸的士<br />\n一星期揸1,2日<br />\n可以有藉口練下車, 見識下人生百態, 又搵到少少外快, 又可以認下路當遊下車河咁去下唔同地方<br />\n平時搭的士見到個的士司機都有諗過其實揸的士好似幾正幾好玩又幫到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗唔諗得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91471b8f47261e5de5f13ea2bee119f3db640d0b","tid":954110,"uid":17506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"你知唔知考的士牌要有1年p+2年正式牌先考得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61db44ca36c43b4c11d0810919f8ea37032075e","tid":954110,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91471b8f47261e5de5f13ea2bee119f3db640d0b","tid":954110,"uid":17506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"你知唔知考的士牌要有1年p+2年正式牌先考得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"知呀 而家諗定姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f3865e6e1deaf5a788fd6190c25980911bb6d9","tid":954110,"uid":124414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91471b8f47261e5de5f13ea2bee119f3db640d0b","tid":954110,"uid":17506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"你知唔知考的士牌要有1年p+2年正式牌先考得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"唔係1年p + 3年正式咩? 原來係2年正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac